Corporate trainer for organizations that focus on leadership, personality styles, professional communication and exceptional customer service.

Hand-picked by Cy Wakeman to deliver keynotes of her Reality-Based Leadership book content and provide development solutions for clients. Cy Wakeman is a dynamic speaker, author and though-leader in the areas of leadership, people management and development. Her philosophies mix common sense practical and humor with the philosophies of Reality-Based Leadership. She speaks at conferences, trains leadership at small and large companies and coaches CEOs and leaders to the next level. Her second book- Reality-Based Rules of the Workplace is a New York Times bestseller. It is an employee guide to becoming a rock star at work though pursuing personal accountability.The philosophies and advice in Cy's first book, Reality-Based Leadership, are available in an internally- directed corporate training program. Visit us at www.realitybasedleadership.com
